    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CrapShoot 是一款侧滚动子弹射击游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款简单的射击游戏，共有 3 个阶段，控制简单，只有慢速和炸弹两种操作。子弹可以通过获取能量道具来增强威力，但如果被击中，就会失去能量，当能量耗尽时游戏就结束了。通过一次又一次的通关来获得最高分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女巫女孩跨坐在扫帚上，向一家便利店走去，但狗粪和凶恶的野生动物挡住了她的去路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款在日本功能手机上大受欢迎的游戏现在推出了一个全新的、略微增强的版本。除了完美的像素画面外，怀旧的光栅滚动也让游戏充满复古气息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251950/extras/564c1f7cc49ea0f7f9574d3c797b14f4.poster.avif?t=1728561609\" width=480 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251950/extras/564c1f7cc49ea0f7f9574d3c797b14f4.webm?t=1728561609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251950/extras/564c1f7cc49ea0f7f9574d3c797b14f4.mp4?t=1728561609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >如何玩</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >慢速和选择 ：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 键、Z 键、回车键、空格键</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速和取消 ：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B键、Esc键、X键、B键、退格键</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >暂停</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开始键、P 键</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >切换全屏 ：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >F11 键</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >取消全屏 ：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Esc 键</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重置 ：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >暂停时长按选择键</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
